1. *Prije* nego što su došli, svi su bili veoma uzbuđeni. (Before they arrived, everyone was very excited.)
2. *Prije* svega, moramo odrediti ciljeve. (First of all, we need to set goals.)
3. *Prije* nego što sam shvatio šta se desilo, bilo je već kasno. (Before I realized what had happened, it was already too late.)
4. *Prije* svega treba da obratimo pažnju na zdravlje. (First of all, we should pay attention to health.)
5. *Prije* samo nekoliko minuta svi su bili srećni. (Just a few minutes ago everyone was happy.)